					<div class="steam_discussions_intro">
						<p><b>Everyone is invited!</b> The Steam discussions are for everyone, new and advanced user alike!</p>
						<p><b>Searching is key!</b> Before you post a question, use the forum search feature to determine whether your topic has already been covered.</p>
						<p><b>Do not start flame wars!</b> If someone has engaged in behavior that is a detriment to the message board -- spamming, flaming people, etc -- contact one of the forum moderators or report the post. Flaming the offensive user will only increase the problem. Harassment is not tolerated.</p>
						<p><b>Looking for the old forums?</b>  They're still available at <a class="whiteLink" href="http://forums.steampowered.com/forums/" target="_blank">http://forums.steampowered.com/forums/</a></p>
